quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  12,30,"Eaba basali har’a motse ba a ts`eha, ba re: “Mosali oa letona o kopa lekhoba la hae ketso e fosahetseng o mo ekela sebeng. Ruri o mo tabotse pelong ka lerato. Etsoe re’a ‘mona hore o pakahatsa a khelohile.”"
  12,31,"Ha mosali eo a utloa lits’ebo tseo tsa bona, a ba mema; o ile a ba etsetsa mokete e le ho tla pakahatsa ka oona, eaba o neha motho ka mong thipa. Eaba moo a ileng a re ho Josefa: “Tsoela sebaeeng ba u bone! Ha ba ‘mona, ba mo rorisa hoo ba ileng ba its’eha matsoho, ba re: “Allah U re hauhele! Hona ha se motho oa nama le mali. Hona ha ho moo ho fapanang teng le manyeloi.”"
  12,32,"Mosali eo a re: “Ke enoa he! Monna eo le ileng la mpeha molato ka eena. Ke ile ka mo kopa ketso e fosahetseng, empa o ile a paka boits’oaro, hajoale ha a sa phethahatse taelo ea ka, Ruri o tla koalloa chankaneng, Ruri o tla nyenyefatsoa.”"
  12,33,"A re: “Mong`a ka! Chankane ebile e molemo ho feta sena seo ba ‘memelang sona, kantle le haeba uena o ka khelosa maraba ana a bona ho ‘na, nka ts’oha ka sekamela ka ho bona, ka fetoha leoatla.”"
  12,34,"Mong`a hae A utloa thapelo ea hae, A mo phemisa maraba a bona. Hobane Ruri U utloa tsohle, U Tseba lintho tsohle"
  12,35,"Ho ile ha hlaka mahlong a banna, kamor’a hoba ba bone lits’upiso tsa ho loka ha hae ho mo koalla chankaneng ha nakoana"
  12,36,"Eaba ho etsahala hore a koalloe le banna ba ba beli. Ke moo ka le leng e mong a ileng a re: “Ke lorile ke tlhotla veine.” E mong eena o re: “‘Na ke lorile ke roetse seroto sa bohobe hlohong ea ka, linonyana li eja bohobe boo. Joale ak’u re manollele tlhaloso ea tsona, hobane re’a u bona hore u har’a ba etsang botle"
  12,37,"Josefa a re: “Ke tla le bolella tlhaloso ea tsona pele le fumana lijo tsa lona tsa letsatsi ka leng le pele li ka le oela. Sena ke karolo ea ts’ebetso eo Mong`a ka a nthutileng eona. Ke furaletse tumelo ea batho ba sa kholoeng ho Allah ba bile ba latola bophelo Bo-tlang"
  12,38,"Ke latela litsela tsa bo-ntate, – Abrahama, Isaaka le Jakobo. Re ke ke ra kopanya batlatsetsi le Allah. Sena ke nala ea Allah ho rona le ho batho bohle; le hoja batho ba bangata ba sa fane ka liteboho"
  12,39,"Oho balekane ba ka ba ba beli ba bats’oaruoa! Na marena a mangata a molemo, kapa ke Allah ea inotsi, ea matla oohle"
  12,40,"Bao le ba khumamelang ntle ho Eena ha se letho haese mabitso ao le ba rehileng ona, lona le bo-ntat’a lona. Allah ha A e s’o senole matla ho ona. Qeto ke ea Allah feela, Eena ea le laetseng hore ho se be ope eo le mo rapelang ntle ho Eena. Ena ke eona tumelo e nepahetseng, empa bongata ba batho ha ba tsebe letho"
  12,41,"Lona balekane ba ka ba ba beli ba bats’oaruoa! E mong oa lona, u tla qhatsetsa morena oa hae veine e mong eena, o tla thakhisoa sefapanong hore linonyana li tle li jelle hloohong ea hae. Ke ka mokhoa oo taba eo e ahloloang kateng mabapi le seo le neng le botsa ka sona.”"
  12,42,"Eaba o re ho e mong bobeling boo, a neng a tseba hore o tla pholosoa: “u tle u tsebise Mong`a hau ka ‘na.” Empa Satane o ile a etsa hore a lebale ho tsebisa Mong`a hae ka eena, eaba Josefa o hlola chankaneng ka lilemo tse seng kae"
  12,43,"Motlotlehi(oa Egepeta) o re: “Ke lorile ke bona likhomo tse nonneng tse supileng, li jeoa ke likhomo tse supileng tse otileng; le litsejana tse supileng tse talana tsa koro ekasitana le tse supileng tse bajooeng. Oho lona matona! Ntlhalosetseng toro ea ka, haeba le ka khona ho hlalosa litoro.”"
  12,44,"Ba re: “Tlhakants’uts’u ea litoro! Rona ha re tsebe ho manolla le hona ho hlalosa litoro"
  12,45,"Eaba monna e mong oa bobeli ebile e le oa ho lopolloa chankaneng, o hopola Josefa kamor’a nako, a re: “Ke tla u joetsa tlhaloso ea eona ha feela eba u ka nthoma ho ea e lata.”"
  12,46,"Hoba a fihle ho Josefa chankaneng, a re: “Oho Josefa! Uena ea nang le ‘nete! A k’u re rarollele toro ea likhomo tse supileng tse nonneng, tse jeoang ke tse otileng tse supileng le litsejana tsa koro tse supileng tse talana le tse supileng tse bajuoeng, hore ke tle ke boele ho batho; battle ba tsebe"
  12,47,"Josefa a re: “le tla lema ka lilemo tse supileng joaloka ka mehla, empa seo le tla beng le se kotutse le se tlohele se sa poloa, haese se senyenyane seo le tla seja"
  12,48,"Joale kamor’a moo, ho tla tla lilemo tse supileng tsa tlala tse tla metsa tsohle tseo le tla beng le ile la li lokisa e sa le pele, haese se fokolang seo le ileng la ipokella sona"
  12,49,"Kamor’a moo, ho tla latela selemo seo batho ba tla bale chai e ngata hoo ba tla beng ba tlhotle veine le mafura.”"
  12,50,"Eaba Motlotlehi o re: “Ntlisetseng eena koano mona.” Empa ea romileng hoba a fihle ho eena, eaba Josefa o re: “Boela ho Mong`a hau, u ‘motse ka taba ea basali bane ba ho its’eha matsoho. Bona! Ruri Mong`a ka o tseba leraba la bona"
  12,51,"Eaba Motlotlehi o bitsa basali bao, a re: “Ho ne ho etsahetse joang ha le tla be le hohelle Josefa ketsong ea sebe? Ba araba ka hore: “Allah a ke a ‘moloke! Rona ha ho sebe seo re se tsebang malebana le eena. Eaba mosali oa letona le leholo o re: “Hajoale ‘nete e pepeneneng. Nkile ka mo kopa ketso ea sebe, Ruri u har’a ba nang le ‘nete.”"
  12,52,"Josefa a re: “Ke kopile sena, e le hore Mong`a ka a tle a tsebe hore ha ke’a ka ka mo seolla sephiring, etsoe Ruri Allah ha a tataise leraba la maoatla"